graph TD
    A[Analyst Initiates Query] --> B{Input Rails Check}
    B -- Fails --> C[Reject: Prompt Injection/Jailbreak]
    B -- Passes --> D[Retrieve SEC Filings & Knowledge Graph]
    
    D --> E{Retrieval Rails Check}
    E -- Irrelevant --> F[Reject/Refine Search]
    E -- Relevant --> G[Extract Financial Facts]
    
    G --> H[XBRL Cross-Validation]
    H --> I[Semantic Validation]
    
    I --> J{Confidence Scorer}
    J -- High Confidence --> K[AUTO: Direct to Math Node]
    J -- Medium Confidence --> L[SAMPLED_REVIEW: Queue for HITL]
    J -- Low/Trigger Fired --> M[ESCALATE: Require Manual Override]
    
    K --> N[Deterministic Math Execution]
    L --> N
    M -- Analyst Approves --> N
    
    N --> O{Execution & Output Rails}
    O -- Fails --> P[Abstain / Mask PII]
    O -- Passes --> Q[Deliver Auditable Answer]
    
    Q --> R[Metrics Dashboard & Drift Monitoring]
